item.title: CVE-2020-1826|2024-08-04T06:46:30.919Z -- huawei -- honor%20magic2
item.description: Huawei Honor Magic2 mobile phones with versions earlier than 10.0.0.175(C00E59R2P11) have an information leak vulnerability. Due to a module using weak encryption tool, an attacker with the root permission may exploit the vulnerability to obtain some information.
